c: 2
v: 285
t: "Intumwa (Muhamadi) yemeye ibyoyahishuriwe biturutse kwa Nyagasani wayo ndetse n’abemera (barabyemeye). Buri wese yemeye Allah, abamalayika be, ibitabo byen’intumwa ze; (bavuga bati) \"Nta n’imwe turobanura mu ntumwa Baranavuga bati \"Twumvise kandi ze\". twumviye. (Turagusaba) imbabazi, Nyagasani wacu! Kandi iwawe ni ho byose bizasubira"